snippet.title: Infinite Adventures Story Trailer : PS4®, Xbox One, Steam
snippet.description:
You are the Traveler, a hero with a forgotten memory. Explore the Infinite Labyrinth to discover the truths of your past.

In the years before the Awakening,
A great discovery was made.

On the solemn outskirts of town,
The Traveler emerged from the Infinite Labyrinth.

Many from around the world of Trinity came,
Nobles and commoners, high born and low.

Some sought glory for their house,
Others sought riches and fame.

If only they knew evil would awaken,
What Infinite Adventures lie in the depths.

"Chronicles of the Age of Man" Vol VII : The Awakening
by Justice Carmathil XIV, Adjutant General of House Carmathil
